  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment performed. This adversarial package carries a rebutting defeater: the hasDecisionRecord outcome is Accepted while the Model Form credibility factor reports achievedLevel 2 against a requiredLevel 3, a structural shortfall that the rationale obscures through extended expert-judgment language.",
